This repository includes a modified derivative of the GitHub Codex plugin
example distributed in OpenAI's plugin example collection.

Original upstream source:
- https://github.com/openai/plugins

Derivative work in this repository:
- adapts the GitHub plugin to Codex API mode
- replaces ChatGPT app login dependency with local GitHub CLI (`gh`) workflows
- adds retry and fallback behavior for unstable GitHub API transport scenarios
- adds repository-level marketplace metadata, installation scripts, and public docs

